ast.value: step       - execute until another function in on the top of the stack
up        - move up in the stack trace
down      - move down in the stack trace
vars      - display variables in the current stack frame
stack     - display all functions on the call stack
print var - display the value of variable named 'var' in the current stack frame
pidx  idx - display the value of variable at position #idx in the current stack frame
break fn  - add breakpoint for fn
